Package abyss.utilities

Class Whirlpool

java.lang.Object
abyss.utilities.Whirlpool
public class Whirlpool extends Object
The Whirlpool hashing function.

References

The Whirlpool algorithm was developed by Paulo S. L. M. Barreto and Vincent Rijmen.

See P.S.L.M. Barreto, V. Rijmen, ``The Whirlpool hashing function,'' First NESSIE workshop, 2000 (tweaked version, 2003), invalid input: '<'https://www.cosic.esat.kuleuven .ac.be/nessie/workshop/submissions/whirlpool.zip>

      Delivers input data to the hashing algorithm.
      Parameters:
      source - plaintext data to hash.
      sourceBits - how many bits of plaintext to process.

      This method maintains the invariant: bufferBits invalid input: '<' 512
